entities.name: ElizaOS
entities.description: A project focused on AI and blockchain technology. Its ecosystem includes the ElizaOS token and related products like Cloud MVP.

entities.name: AI16Z
entities.description: A deprecated cryptocurrency token associated with the ElizaOS ecosystem. It was superseded by the ELIZAOS token.

entities.name: ELIZAOS
entities.description: The primary cryptocurrency token of the ElizaOS ecosystem. It is intended for future utility within ElizaOS products.

entities.name: X
entities.description: A social media platform, formerly known as Twitter, used for communication and potential partnerships within the ElizaOS project.

entities.name: Cloud MVP
entities.description: A Minimum Viable Product for a cloud-based service within the ElizaOS ecosystem. It is designed to showcase initial product capabilities.

entities.name: Discord

entities.name: GitHub
entities.description: A platform for software development and version control, used by the ElizaOS team for managing their codebase and releases.

entities.name: TradingView
entities.description: A charting platform and social network for traders and investors, which the ElizaOS community requested integration with for improved chart functionality.

entities.name: Playwright
entities.description: An open-source toolchain for automated testing and web scraping, used in discussions for comparing with ElizaOS's capabilities.

entities.name: Puppeteer
entities.description: A Node.js library providing a high-level API to control Chrome or Chromium over the DevTools Protocol, used in discussions for comparison with ElizaOS.

entities.name: Starknet
